You can replace the backing plate.  It will have new clips on it, I think.
$99/pair at Bus Depot.   You can buy a used clip from BustedBus for $5.  I
am not sure how it gets attached, some kind of rivet.  I worry about this
happening to me too, so far it has not happened yet.

